  "content": "There is a complex, bilateral adnexal mass with mixed solid and cystic components. Trace ascites is present. Multiple soft tissue peritoneal implants are noted along the paracolic gutters and in the left upper quadrant adjacent to the spleen. These findings are suggestive of primary ovarian carcinoma with peritoneal spread. Recommend CA-125 and referral to gynecologic oncology.",
